<plot>Kitty still loved her husband in spite of his name. In spite of the orchard that called him away from her. Once she thought they might relive dreams under sun drenched trees. Once she thought she loved him best from another man's bed. Now that other man threatens to reveal his secret and the trees fail to shelter dreamers. And after it all, the sun still sets on Golden Afternoons.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?218939</url></doc>
